<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3527576>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Map showing the known distribution of Polypedates bengalensis sp. nov. Grey circle: Khordanahala, District: 24 Parganas South; black circle: Madhyamgram, District: 24 Parganas North." ;
