<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3527592>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Axillary amplexus shown by a pair of Polypedates bengalensis sp. nov. (unpreserved) in Khordanahala, 24 Parganas, West Bengal, India." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3527592/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3527594>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Maximum likelihood phylogeny based on DNA sequences of the mitochondrial gene for 16s rRNA, showing the relationship of Polypedates bengalensis sp. nov. and its congeners, with Rhacophorus rhodopus as the outgroup. The values at nodes are bootstrap support values." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3527594/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

